title: Walking Dead S:5 | E:15 Try | Slate TV Club
description:
Mike Vuolo and Chris Wade recap Episode 15 of The Walking Dead, “Try.”
 
Mike is the host ofSlate's Lexicon Valley podcast and a senior producer forSlatepodcasts, and Chris is a producer for theSlate Video team.
 
Slate Plus members can download an ad-free version of Slate’s Walking Dead podcast. To learn more and to try Slate Plus free for two weeks, visit Slate.com/DeadPlus.
